You will deal +{{%01%}}% damage for every point spent in the Cybernetic tree.
You can take a skill up to level 3 once you've spent {{%01%}} points in its skill tree.
Used to unlock multiple skill trees.
Used to unlock multiple skill trees.
Used to unlock multiple skill trees.
Restores your health whenever you deal damage to enemies.
Increases your out of combat healing speed and triggers this sooner.
Blocks enemy bullets. Upon expiry your Force Field explodes to damage nearby enemies.
Makes you invisible to enemies while standing far away from them.
You'll briefly deal less damage and drain mana over time.

source: Slows the speed of enemy bullets. Your bullets will also seek towards enemies.
Increases your rate of fire. This also applies to nearby allies when you cast it.
Bursts out deadly blades that bounce off walls and damage nearby enemies.
Shocks all enemy players and bullets in front of you. Shocked enemies will be revealed, and bullets you shock will freeze in mid-air.
Creates a large radioactive field on the ground that damages enemies over time.
Fires a dart that poisons enemies, slowly damaging them over time.
Launches an explosive ball of plasma that gains damage the further it travels.
Protects you from enemy weapon damage whenever you cast a skill.
You'll do less damage for longer.
Bounces bullets off your force field.
Reduces the damage of your force field explosion.
Creates a spinning vortex on the ground that sucks in and slows enemies.
Improves your reload and weapon swapping speed.
Reveals nearby enemies through walls. Your allies will also see these enemies.
Makes your bullets bounce off walls.
Slows the movement speed of all enemies within your radiation field.
Throws a line of spikes onto the ground when you cast Blade Fury. These spikes damage all enemies and vehicles that cross them.
Reduces the number of Blade Fury blades.
Blocks all non-weapon damage and negative status effects. You will also gain health from enemy non-weapon damage.
Throws a smoke bomb on the ground when you cast Black Hole, which causes your enemies' screens to fade to black.
Reduces the strength of Black Hole's slow.
Steals enemy bullets and seeks them back towards your enemies. This triggers the moment Bullet Time is disabled.
target: Düşman mermilerini çalıp düşmanlarına geri gönderir. Bullet Time aktif değilken başlar.

source: Increases your ammo whenever you hit an enemy and have Frenzy active.
target: Frenzy aktifken düşman vurulduğunda mermi sayısını arttırır.

source: Teleports you to a targetted location after a short channelling time.
target: Kısa bir odaklanma süresinden sonra seni hedeflenmiş bir konuma ışınlar.

source: Whenever you kill a shocked enemy you'll gain a charge that regenerates your health.

Your venom dart will seek slower.
target: Zehir dartın daha kısa süre arayacak.

source: Summons an orb that increases the damage of your bullets when they fly through it. Does not work while someone stands within it.

Creates a clone of you that confuses enemies when you leave invisibility.

source: Pretty awful as a car. But it's cheap and makes a nice step for jumping over walls.
target: Vasıta olarak berbat ancak ucuz ve duvarları turmanmak için iyi bir basamak görevi görür.

source: Fast and agile - just watch out for the low health. If it catches on fire you'll burn.
Fast and durable - a great all-rounder. Can even withstand a direct shot from a Bazooka!
A good combat vehicle great for co-op drivebys. Press [F3] to hop into the back seat.
Has a radar the reveals the location of nearby enemies. Lets you see through walls and spy on your enemies' movements!
Very durable for its price and with 6 seats it's great for co-op drivebys.
Fastest car in the game! Press [SHIFT] to boost and Tokyo Drift all over the place.
Comes with a ticking time bomb. [Left click] to toggle the timer on and off, but make sure you hop out before it explodes!
A huge truck with massive health and 5 passenger seats. The back 3 seats allow for a full 360 degree shooting range.
target: Çok canı ve 5 yan koltuğu olan kocaman bir kamyon. Arkadaki 3 koltuğu tam 360 derece bir ateş alanı yaratır. Çok pahalı ama dostlar ile sen nerdeyse durdurulamazsın!

source: [Left Click] to fire 2 homing missiles that deal huge damage against vehicles and zombies.
Drive the Extraction Truck to its extraction zone.
[Left Click] to fire a deadly flamethrower. The Cybertruck is shatterproof.
Silent and deadly. The knife kills enemies in a single shot.
Kaboom! This deals huge damage if it explodes at your enemies feet.
Explodes with a huge flash of light that blinds nearby enemies for a few seconds. Minimise your own flash by taking cover as it explodes.
Fires a missile that deals huge damage against vehicles and zombies.
A silenced pistol with good accuracy.
target: Güzel keskin susturuculu bir tabanca. Ateş ettiğinde yakındaki muhafızlar duymaz.

source: High damage and rate of fire makes this a great sidearm - just watch out for the low ammo.
An extremely mobile superweapon that slows enemies.
A great run & gun weapon with the fastest movement speed in the game.
A high rof and high movement speed make this a great all-round weapon.
A high damage superweapon. Its bullets will bounce off walls and pierce through enemies.
Does huge damage at point blank range.
An auto-shotgun with huge close range DPS. Charge up close and blast your enemies away!

An extremely powerful superweapon that fires explosive bullets. You can lob these bullets over walls to attack unsuspecting victims. You can also blast yourself up into the air with its explosive force by aiming at your feet.
Very effective at range, but you'll need to burst fire to control its recoil.
Accurate and great at range. It's silenced so nearby guards won't hear you fire it.

Has a huge clip size and deals extra vehicle damage.
Has a huge clip size with high damage, You'll move super slow though.
An extremely high damage superweapon that deals extra damage against vehicles.
Gives you an extended scope to see further and snipe enemies off screen.

Tosses a flaming bottle that explodes on impact. These flames persist and deal damage to anything that travels through them.
Fires a flare that explodes on impact, like a mini bazooka.
An extremely deadly superweapon that shoots fire and ignites anything it touches.

Nearby allies support you by slowly regenerating your mana and health.
target: Yakındaki dostlarınız sizin büyünüzü ve canınızı artırarak yardım ediyorlar.

source: Hover here to view the skills menu.
Left click skills to add them. Right click to view them.
Click 'Start Adding Skills' to create a skill build.
If you die you'll become a zombie. You can resurrect by killing a survivor or finding the Heart.
Press ({{%01%}}) to chat. Say 'wassup' to receive a bonus 10xp!
Kills raise your mutant level. This unlocks skills in your skill build.
Head to a buy zone, press ({{%01%}}), and click the yellow 'Buy Ammo' button. You can do this very quickly.
Enter a car by pressing ({{%01%}}), then kill someone in a driveby shooting.
Hold ({{%01%}}) and click 'Reset Skill Build' from the drop-down skills menu up the top of the screen.
Spend 2 skill points on 'Plasma Ball'. Right click skills to queue up future points, so they automatically unlock whenever you level up.
Click ({{%01%}}) to heal with the 'Self Repair' skill. Your mana and active skills are shown below.
This is the Outbreak game mode. To win you need to kill zombies, collect their souls and return them to the bomb.
After collecting souls you need to return them to the bomb. Follow the arrow on your screen to take your souls to the bomb. Hold (TAB) to see your score.
target: Ruh topladıkdan sonra bombaya geri getirmeniz gerekiyor. Her ruh karşılığında skor, para, büyü, can ve deneyim kazanıcaksınız. Ekranınızdaki oku takip edip bombaya geri getirin. (TAB)'a basılı tutarak skorunuzu görün.

source: Cash (shown above) lets you buy guns. Get kills to save up $5000.
Buy the 'Synthetic Shop' chemical. When you carry this chemical, your ammo will last longer.
Place 'Synthetic Shop' with ({{%01%}}). This create a buy zone for you and your allies.
Stand in your 'Synthetic Shop' and press ({{%01%}}) and buy ammo.
Pick up your chemical by standing in it and pressing ({{%01%}}).
This is the Conquest game mode where you need to capture all of the Control Points in the map. You can do this extra fast with the 'Capturer' chemical. Buy a 'Capturer' chemical from a buy zone.
Capture a point by holding ({{%01%}}) and placing your Capturer on the very center point of it.
This is the Extraction game mode. Follow the white arrow on your screen to capture the enemy flag.
Follow the arrow and take the flag to the enemy flag near your spawn. Hold (TAB) to see your score.
This is the Checkpoint game mode. To win you need do laps with the Battery in a vehicle. Grab a car, then follow the white arrow on your screen to pick up the Battery.
Follow the white arrow on your screen to drive the battery through each of the checkpoints. Hold (TAB) to see your score.
Stand inside an enemy chemical, hold ({{%01%}}), and select 'Neutralize Chemicals' to destroy it.
Press (F10) to finish this tutorial. This opens the How to Play Guide if you want to learn more.
Your goal is to win {{%03%}} rounds. Try to survive the rest of this round. Follow the arrow to the safe zone.
Always buy a better gun! Go to a buy zone (yellow on the map), then press ({{%01%}}) and buy the MP5.
Open a blue supply crate by shifting into it. Press ({{%01%}}) to shift.
Double tap ({{%01%}}) to drift. This lets you move faster. Your shifts are shown under your health bar.
Now let's give bots full damage... Survive this round to win the game!
Select your knife with ({{%01%}}) and hold fire to charge it. Once you turn red you can kill in a single shot.
Find a civilian with a green text bubble above him and press ({{%01%}}).
Mission info is shown above the minimap. Complete them to gain cash and powerful bonuses.
Learn to play and earn bonus XP!
The player count, timer, and your score are shown here.
Your health, mana and shifts are shown down here.
Press 1, 2, 3 to select weapons, and middle mouse to throw grenades.
Press Right Mouse, C & F to cast skills. Hold ALT to spend skill points.
to toggle this guide on and off.

The meaning of life, the universe and everything you need to know about Geneshift can be found in this guide; so toggle this back on when you're ready to play like a pro. Until then you can press ENTER to chat with the server and ask questions. Have fun!
I JUST WANT TO STOP DYING!!
EARN A LITTLE EXTRA ON THE SIDE..
What do I have to do?
Follow the arrow on your screen to reach the next checkpoint. Try to earn combo kills to gain extra cash.
What if I miss some text?
Press (ENTER) to bring up the chat log. The green lines have important tips. Also when playing singleplayer you can hold (ALT) to pause the game and read the text at your own pace.
Stay out of combat for a few seconds to trigger auto-heal. Use vehicles for protection while looting. Unlock healing skills with (ALT). Buy expensive weapons to deal extra damage.
target: Kendini iyileştirmek için kısa bir süre boyunca mücadeleden uzak dur. Yuvarlar kontrol noktaların içinde iken silah satın al (B). Son olarak, İyileştirme yetenekleri aç (ALT) ve Sağ Tık, C ve Z'ye basarak kullan.

source: You simply gain +1 score per round that you win. First to win enough rounds wins the match.
Avoid the circle of death and try to stay alive. Survival is key! If you become a zombie use this time to loot for cash. Or try resurrect with the Genetic Heart or by killing a survivor.

When you view the skills page through the main menu you're looking at your permanent skill build. This build is only used in permanent multiplayer servers and persists between rounds. This build is not used in quickmatches or the campaign.
Here you can host multiplayer modes and play against bots. To play against humans it's usually better to join an official server.
You can improve your FPS by updating your graphics drivers. For now, would you like Geneshift to optimise your graphics settings?
No. The human eye can only see 30 FPS.
requires a manual download. Go to www.geneshift.net and get it now!

We'll take you to him... Just step in here...
target: Seni ona götüreceğiz... Sadece şuraya gir...

source: We're not giving you shit. Now if you're done monologuing...
target: Sana hiçbir şey vermeyeceğiz. Şimdi, kendinle konuşman bittiyse...

source: We're not here to play games. We're here to stop you.
target: Biz oyun oynamak için değil; seni durdurmak için buradayız.

source: We're trying! But he's a super mutant. That's the whole point!
target: Deniyoruz! Ama o bir süper mutant. Tüm mesele bu!

source: We've already play-tested so many skills...
We've gotta get these civilians outta here.
We've run the test so many times...
Well he's proven himself. So for the love of God kill him.
Well let us help. I wanna test these sweet blades!
Well my friend does most of the actual killing..
Well that's just asking to be explored!
Welp, this is it. The final showdown.
What a twist! HQ drugged the Rebels.
What are they doing anyway.. they're just walking in circles.
What the hell is going on up here?
What the hell!? Johnson, get out here!
What the.. how'd you do that?
What's the matter buddy? Are you ok?
What, drugging the Rebels? It's for the greater good.
When fuelled by violence.. It's such a rush!
Where is HQ? Where do you make the water?!
Why I oughta... I'll teach them a thing or two!
Why are the Rebels doing all this anyway?
Why do they call us.. test-subjects?
Woop woop. The boss is here!
Yeah but there are hundreds of us.
Yeah sorry about that throw. I'm not very coordinated.
target: O atış için üzgünüm. Pek koordineli değilim.

source: Yeah, but it's cool.. They're a lot of fun.
Yeah, but then the Rebels went crazy.. and you have too!
target: Evet ancak, asiler delirdi.. ve sen de!

source: Yeauk this water stinks! What is HQ doing down here?
target: Iyy bu su iğrenç kokuyor! Karargahın orada ne işi var?

source: Yes!! C'mon man we're saving the world here!
target: Evet!! Haydi dostum, burada dünyayı kurtarıyoruz!

source: You beat me at my own game...
You can use this to teleport directly to the bomb.
You could've opened that door a bit earlier..
You damn fools! You don't know what -
You drugged the Rebels and sent them insane. Why??
target: Asilere ilaç verip delirttin mi? Neden??

source: You go ahead. Try not to get bit.
You ready? Click the blue arrow up top and let's warp outta here!
target: Hazır mısın? Yukarıdaki mavi oka bas ve buradan gidelim!

source: You saved me! Take this cash as thanks.
target: Beni kurtardın! Bu parayı teşekkür olarak kabul et.

source: You sure you don't want to join us?
You want me to open that door down there?
You'll do WHAT to my mother!?
You're not going to start monologuing, are you?
You're not like these other weaklings.
You're too cliche for me. Now take this!
You're too late - the clones are free!
You've got skills man. That cape suits you.
target: Yeteneklerin var dostum. Bu pelerin sana yakışmış.

source: You've knocked those zombies off the rails! Don't run out of steam!
Your game has worked a little too well...
[Left Click] to fire the stinger missiles.
